I can also confirm that the repo [link](https://github.com/tensorflow/models) in the tutorial does not link to the file that you [referenced](https://github.com/tensorflow/models/tree/master/tutorials/rnn/ptb).  Thank you for providing.  I will note that that code, as a tutorial example, is somewhat opaque.
